div.p:
—The local and foreign press (the latter despite my pointing out the openings
                    which remain) have cast the responses of the government and FAO toward the NG
                    proposal as a total rejection;

—Making clear that a grave responsibility falls on the GON, the FAO and all groups
                    actively involved in the search for a solution if they do not take advantage of
                    the mediation effort to avoid further deterioration of the situation;
